    S_EXPONENTS          16.00  8.00  1.83  0.60  0.06  
    P_EXPONENTS          13.00  2.50  0.75
  &END PP_BASIS

  &POTENTIAL
    PSEUDO_TYPE GTH
    &GTH_POTENTIAL
    3    6    0    0
    0.21845674097331       3   -0.11598011360544   -0.58386001845049    0.11900246932074
       2
    0.13956354907332       1   34.80407754306934
    0.13189580696310       1  -13.99739306305770
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 10.0 
  &END POTENTIAL

  &POWELL
     ACCURACY   1.e-14
     STEP_SIZE  0.1
     MAX_FUN    50000
  &END
&END ATOM
